In the Matter of Andrew C. Levine (Admitted as Andrew Charles Levine), a Suspended Attorney.

[— NYS2d —]

Motion granted and respondent reinstated as an attorney and counselor-at-law in the State of New York, effective im*283mediately. No opinion. Concur—Sullivan, J. P., Rosenberger, Wallach, Tom and Andrias, JJ.
